      • increaseTotalPrice

        public static double increaseTotalPrice(java.util.ArrayList<Books> st,
                        boolean nfict,
                        boolean fict)
        When users click the Increase price button, the GUI will invoke this method to increase the prices of selected Book categories, and the new total price will be displayed on the GUI
        Parameters:
        st - the list of all added Books
        nfict - the state of the checkbox of NonFiction, if the checkbox of NonFiction is checked, then nfict is true
        fict - the state of the checkbox of Fiction, if the checkbox of Fiction is checked, then fict is true
        Returns:
        the new total prices of all the Books in the list after increased
